  "pioneer-pet-vs-yeapaw": {
    title: "Pioneer Pet Raindrop vs YEAPAW (2026) — Budget Classic or Premium Pumpless?",
    description: "Pioneer Pet Raindrop vs YEAPAW Stainless Steel Fountain head-to-head. We compare price, noise, capacity, cleaning ease, and which stainless steel cat fountain offers the best value in 2026.",
    winner: "The Pioneer Pet Raindrop wins for most cat owners — at $39 with 18,500+ reviews, it's the proven classic with dishwasher-safe convenience and a whisper-quiet pump. The YEAPAW at $93 is the premium choice for owners who want zero plastic contact and a pumpless design that's virtually silent. If budget and track record matter most, Pioneer Pet. If you want the cleanest, quietest fountain and don't mind paying 2.4x more, YEAPAW is the future.",
